her you could not get your visa in time or due to an error of the part of the embassy / consulate, an incorrect visa is issued to you, you shall have the option to postpone your tour to any other future date Or tranFfer your too r to any other tour and In such case the amendment fee for shall apply, in addition to cancellation charges.
